== 汉字转拼音 version 0.0.1
	Chinese Pinyin conversion. => Elvuel::Hz2Py

== 繁简转换
	Chinese traditional and simplified conversion. => Elvuel::TraditionalAndSimplified

== Example

	Hz2Py.do("你好") => "ni hao"
	TraditionalAndSimplified.conv_t2s("鳳凰") => "凤凰"
	TraditionalAndSimplified.conv_s2t("无心插柳柳成阴") => "無心插柳柳成陰"

== Rspec
	spec test/hz2py_test.rb
	spec test/ts_test.rb

